{
  "stem": "3973.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These-- these things stick pretty closely in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They marched in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father and I, he took me for a walk, just to see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans were marching and setting up the narrow streets in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were setting up one-way signs and all kinds of other things which didn't exist before and directed traffic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, this was very exciting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At this point, there was no problem at all, as far as the-- the German army interfering.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my-- my tragedy that day was that I had a watch-- my first watch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had pulled the stem out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It stuck in my mind as the-- the bad part of the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's interesting, because things happened so gradually that you start from the-- this kind of a basis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's just unimaginable how things have really changed, and how fast they began to change.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next day, I saw down the street the German soldiers took some Jewish people with beards, and were cutting them off with scissors, cutting them off sometimes on one side only, or the other.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember there was one Jewish man, Hassidic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they cut his beard, and at the same time cut into his face and was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It sort of shocked me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The school was open until December, or end of November.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I still went about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just began my sixth grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And things were going sort of normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then came the changes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Began-- began to happen very rapidly afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
